  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Gear-Pair</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Gear-Pair</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddGearPair">Add Gear-Pair</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Terminology and definitions:</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="5" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:150px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Gear Mesh : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Inter-locking gear-teeth that allow a torque and motion to be transmitted from one shaft to a different shaft.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:150px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">External Gear Mesh : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The gears have teeth that engage and diverge out from their centers-of-rotation.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:150px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Internal Mesh : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">One of the gears has teeth that converge into its center-of-rotation.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:150px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Simple Gear-Pair : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Two gears that rotate about two fixed centers.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:150px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Epicyclic Gear-Pair : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">One gear rotates about its own center AND its center also orbits around the center of the other gear.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">How to open the Gear-Pair dialog</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:240px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-GEARPAIR-EDIT.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Example External Gear-Pair]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Edit the<text styleclass="Element"> Gear-Pair</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Double-click a </text><text styleclass="Element">Gear-Pair </text><text styleclass="Body Text">in the graphics-area or </text><text styleclass="Interface">Assembly-Tree</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-How-to-Open-a-Dialog-Box" styleclass="SeeAlso">How to Open a dialog</link><text styleclass="VariableName"> &#160;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal">The <text styleclass="Element">Gear-Pair dialog</text> is now open.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><anchor id="Gear-PairDialog"><keywords><keyword>Gear-Pair dialog</keyword></keywords></anchor>Gear-Pair dialog</para>
